- Testing:         Vitest
- Node:            >=20

## Commands

```bash
pnpm install               # install all workspaces
pnpm dev                   # start at localhost:3000
pnpm build                 # build all packages + apps
pnpm lint                  # lint all workspaces
pnpm typecheck             # tsc across all packages
pnpm test                  # run all Vitest tests
```

